post.content:
Hi Parents,

Welcome to Contest Season! This Friday's home game against Wadsworth is quickly followed by our first Band Contest in Nordonia! Here is the link to the Director's Page . Bookmark this page for the remainder of the marching season and check it at least once a week for important information.

See you on Friday! But more importantly, see you on Saturday at our first competition. The ROYALTON letters are ready!

Holly Michalke
